title_bed_bats_review: Bed and breakfast in Siliguri · 1 bedroom · 1 bed · 1 bath
listing_description:
Your home away from home, Maria's Homestay in Siliguri offers tranquility & charm.

While the master bedroom will be all yours, with an attached bath, you'll have access to a fully-functional common kitchen, a drawing room, and a dining area. 

The gateway to Northeast India, Siliguri is the perfect pit stop for you, when you plan to venture into the land of undulating scenic beauty. Similarly, if you belong to the hills and wish to come down to Siliguri, this is the perfect home for you.
